Did you try changing from
```xml
&lt;transformer implementation=&quot;org.apache.maven.plugins.shade.resource.AppendingTransformer&quot;&gt;
    &lt;resource&gt;META-INF/services/javax.ws.rs.ext.Providers&lt;/resource&gt;
&lt;/transformer&gt;
```

to

```xml
&lt;transformer implementation=&quot;org.apache.maven.plugins.shade.resource.AppendingTransformer&quot;&gt;
    &lt;resource&gt;META-INF/services/jakarta.ws.rs.ext.Providers&lt;/resource&gt;
&lt;/transformer&gt;
```

Both files were renamed in resteasy-client and resteasy-jackson2-provider from `javax.ws.rs.ext.Providers` to `jakarta.ws.rs.ext.Providers`

See [here][1] for resteasy-client and [here][2] for resteasy-jackson2-provider

  [1]: https://github.com/resteasy/resteasy/blob/main/resteasy-client/src/main/resources/META-INF/services/jakarta.ws.rs.ext.Providers
  [2]: https://github.com/resteasy/resteasy/blob/main/providers/jackson2/src/main/resources/META-INF/services/jakarta.ws.rs.ext.Providers

