SSNs=[ssn1, ssn2, ssn3]
IDs=[1, 2, 3]
```
Note the type witnessing `&lt;Entry&lt;String, Object&gt;&gt;` for the `mapMulti` method.  In many cases, it is required as the compiler cannot determine the resulting type to be placed on the stream.

